b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Sunsama and Todoist share a solid foundation of core features including Task Management, Ai Assistant, Calendar, Integrations. On the other hand, Todoist uniquely offers Collaboration and Templates, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Sunsama holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Todoist scores 8/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Todoist comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while Sunsama begins at $20/mo. Todoist stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Sunsama requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
